   , (as the beſt affirm (even our Lords Day.

1. To ſtirre freely, with readineſſe and willingneſſe of mind moving about the buſineſſe of Gods bleſſed day;


Though there ſeems difficulty in work, and

Though there is diverſity of work.

6. Inflicting of Cenſures.] This is alſo to be done


Both with a ſpirit of zeal againſt the offending perſon;

And with a ſpirit of love unto the perſon offending.
